tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T20 at the California Qualifying Tournament, shooting rounds of 70-75-75-70...Started his Mackenzie Tour season with a T10 at the PC Financial Open...Finished T12 at the Syncrude Boreal Open.
tourBios.personal: Torrey Pines is his favorite course and hopes to play Cypress Point...Dream foursome would include Tiger Woods, Rory McIlroy and Michael Jordan...Big fan of Los Angeles sports' teams...Twitter is @JamesErkenbeck.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T10th in 2015 at the PC Financial Open.
